
@problemId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Get All Problems
GET http://localhost:4000/api/problems

### Get All Problems with Difficulty Filter
GET http://localhost:4000/api/problems?difficulty=easy

### Get Single Problem
GET http://localhost:4000/api/problems/{{problemId}}

### Create Problem (Admin Only - Requires Auth Cookie)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/problems
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Two Sum",
    "description": "Given an array of integers nums and an integer target, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to target.",
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "tags": ["array", "hash-table"]
}

### Update Problem (Admin Only - Requires Auth Cookie)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/problems/{{problemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Two Sum Updated",
    "difficulty": "medium"
}

### Delete Problem (Admin Only - Requires Auth Cookie)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/problems/{{problemId}}
